# PNPM Only

## Package Manager
Use `pnpm` for all dependency and script commands.

## Disallowed Commands
Do not use `npm`, `yarn`, or `bun` commands in this repository.

## Command Style
- Install dependencies with `pnpm install`
- Run scripts with `pnpm <script>` or `pnpm run <script>`
- Add dependencies with `pnpm add <package>`
- Add dev dependencies with `pnpm add -D <package>`
